        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Chicken Korma. A home-style Indian dish: spices bloomed in fat first, aromatics built up, the long simmer that pulls it together. Adjustable for what you need."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Spices in hot oil first; aromatics second; everything else third. The order matters — it builds the layers that show up at the bowl."
          }
        ]
      },
